{%- comment -%}
  ======================================================
  SKILL: programmatic-seo + schema-markup
  ======================================================

  seo-faq-schema.liquid — FAQPage JSON-LD + HTML visível por produto.

  Lê o metafield `custom.faq_items` (lista de metaobjects com
  campos `question` e `answer`) e renderiza:

  1. FAQPage JSON-LD para rich results no Google (⭐ Featured Snippets)
  2. FAQ accordion HTML acessível para usuários

  COMO ATIVAR:
  1. No Shopify Admin → Conteúdo → Metafields de produto
  2. Criar metafield tipo lista de metaobjects com namespace `custom` e key `faq_items`
  3. Cada metaobject deve ter campos: `question` (texto) e `answer` (texto rico)
  4. Incluir este snippet em qualquer seção de produto com:
     {%- render 'seo-faq-schema', product: product -%}

  ======================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- if product.metafields.custom.faq_items != blank -%}
  {%- assign faq_list = product.metafields.custom.faq_items.value -%}

  {%- comment -%}SKILL: schema-markup | FAQPage JSON-LD via metafield{%- endcomment -%}
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {%- for faq in faq_list -%}
        {%- if faq.question != blank and faq.answer != blank -%}
          {%- unless forloop.first %},{%- endunless -%}
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": {{ faq.question | json }},
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": {{ faq.answer | strip_html | json }}
            }
          }
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    ]
  }
  </script>

  {%- comment -%}SKILL: programmatic-seo | FAQ accordion HTML acessível{%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="seo-faq-section" aria-labelledby="faq-heading-{{ product.id }}">
    <h2 id="faq-heading-{{ product.id }}">Perguntas Frequentes sobre {{ product.title }}</h2>

    <div class="seo-faq-list" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/FAQPage">
      {%- for faq in faq_list -%}
        {%- if faq.question != blank and faq.answer != blank -%}
          <div class="seo-faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
            <details>
              <summary itemprop="name">{{ faq.question }}</summary>
              <div itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                <div itemprop="text" class="seo-faq-answer">
                  {{ faq.answer }}
                </div>
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .seo-faq-section {
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    .seo-faq-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .seo-faq-item {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
    }
    .seo-faq-item details summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 600;
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      position: relative;
      padding-right: 1.5rem;
    }
    .seo-faq-item details summary::-webkit-details-marker {
      display: none;
    }
    .seo-faq-item details summary::after {
      content: '+';
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #666;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    .seo-faq-item details[open] summary::after {
      content: '−';
    }
    .seo-faq-answer {
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
{%- endif -%}
